n%2C%20offices%2C%20located%20a%20few%20blocks%20from%20some%20Amazon%20offices.%20By%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20TikTok%20had%201%2C700%20employees%20there%2C%20according%20to%20the%20city's%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20many%20TikTok%20Shop%20employees%20came%20from%20Amazon%20that%20its%20early%20staff%20meetings%20sometimes%20felt%20like%20Amazon%20alumni%20reunions%2C%20current%20and%20former%20staffers%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20Amazon%20left%2C%20right%2C%20and%20center%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20employee%20who%20came%20from%20Amazon.%20Another%20ex-Amazonian%20estimated%20that%2075%25%20of%20their%202023%20TikTok%20Shop%20orientation%20group%20had%20previously%20worked%20at%20the%20e-commerce%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20showed%20up%20in%20operations%2C%20too.%20TikTok%20team%20members%20routinely%20shared%20insights%20about%20Amazon's%20business%20strategies%2C%20sometimes%20walking%20through%20documents%20taken%20directly%20from%20their%20former%20employer%2C%20two%20current%20staffers%20and%20one%20former%20TikTok%20staffer%20said.%20And%20just%20like%20at%20Amazon%2C%20employees%20crafted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-email-against-powerpoint-presentations-2015-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enarrative%20memos%20to%20share%20products%20or%20ideas%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20allocated%20dedicated%20time%20for%20people%20to%20read%20them.%20Some%20tried%20to%20infuse%20TikTok%20with%20other%20Amazon%20strategies%20like%20customer%20obsession%20or%20single-person%20ownership%20of%20projects%20from%20start%20to%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20exactly%20like%20Amazon%20%E2%80%94%20its%20secret%20sauce%20was%20its%20social%20app%20with%20popular%20videos%20and%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-shop-creators-earning-thousands-affiliate-commissions-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfluencer%2