Vikas%20Khanna%3C%2Fa%3E%20attempted%20to%20perfect%20these%20at%20his%20restaurant%2C%20Bungalow%2C%20in%20New%20York.%20%E2%80%9CBungalow%20is%20a%20celebration%20of%20India.%20It%E2%80%99s%20my%20purpose%20to%20introduce%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20and%20especially%20children%20growing%20up%20in%20the%20West%2C%20now%20second%20and%20third%20generation%20%E2%80%94%20to%20the%20foods%2C%20flavours%2C%20and%20treats%20their%20parents%20and%20grandparents%20grew%20up%20with.%20Our%20nostalgia.%20Our%20rituals.%20Our%20festivals.%20And%20the%20foods%20that%20defined%20them.%20These%20were%20not%20just%20meals%2C%20but%20memories%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%2C%20crediting%20Elloras%20for%20the%20original%20recipe.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDLSUwzbAn6p%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDLSUwzbAn6p%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDLSUwzbAn6p%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Vikas%20Khanna%20(%40vikaskhannagroup)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20clock%20strikes%20eight%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20a%20queue%20begins%20forming%20at%20Elloras.%20Business%20goes%20on%20until%2010%20pm.%20But%2C%20Drona%20shares%2C%20behind%20the%20shutters%2C%20the%20wheels%20are%20chugging%2024%C3%977.%20The%20Elloras%20kitchen%20is%20a%20hive%20of%20activity%3B%20time%20is%20no%20constraint.%20Drona%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20always%20felt%20that%20bakery%20items%20are%20morning%20items%20and%20should%20be%20served%20fresh.%20So%20we%20plan%20in%20a%20way%20that%20our%20production%20continues%20throughout%20the%20night%20so%20that%20when%20we%20open%20our%20outlets%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20everything%20is%20fresh.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20clientele%20at%20Elloras%20is%20proof%20that%20their%20dedication%20is%20paying%20off.%20Among%20those%20who%E2%80%99ve%20stopped%20by%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267757%2Fkapil-dev-world-cup-indian-cricket-captain-success-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eveteran%20cricketers%20Kapil%20Dev%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20MS%20Dhoni%2C%20chef%20Sanjeev%20Kapoor%2C%20the%20Kapoor%20family%2C%20the%20Gandhi%20family%2C%20chief%20ministers%2C%20and%20even%20the%20Maharani%20of%20Patiala.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharani%20visited%20when%20senior%20Gulati%20was%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20things%2C%20in%20the%20bakery%E2%80%99s%20nascent%20days.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20there%20used%20to%20be%20a%20shortage%20of%20Coca-Cola%3B%20you%20had%20to%20book%20in%20advance%20if%20you%20had%20a%20wedding%20in%20the%20house.%20The%20Maharani%20of%20Patiala%20had%20been%20travelling%20along%20the%20Dehradun%20highway%20and%20observed%20that%20Coca-Cola%20was%20being%20sold%20at%20a%20premium%20everywhere.%20Only%20at%20our%20store%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20buy%20it%20at%20MRP%