0supporting%20the%20vine%20and%20harvesting%20the%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20grow%20kantola%20in%2010%20easy%20steps%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Source%20the%20right%20seeds%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStart%20by%20getting%20quality%20%3Cem%3Ekantola%3C%2Fem%3E%20seeds%20or%20tuber%20roots%20from%20a%20local%20nursery%2C%20agro%20shop%2C%20or%20reliable%20online%20vendor.%20Look%20for%20heirloom%20or%20indigenous%20varieties.%20Kantola%20can%20be%20grown%20from%20seeds%20or%20from%20tuberous%20roots%3B%20tubers%20sprout%20quicker%2C%20but%20seeds%20are%20more%20readily%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F612Z27UTnOL._SL1382_-1752155964-500x910.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F612Z27UTnOL._SL1382_-1752155964-500x910.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F612Z27UTnOL._SL1382_-1752155964-165x300.jpg%20165w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F612Z27UTnOL._SL1382_-1752155964-150x273.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F612Z27UTnOL._SL1382_-1752155964.jpg%20759w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-467403%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__content%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Choose%20the%20right%20spot%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKantola%20loves%20warm%20and%20humid%20weather%2C%20and%20monsoon%20provides%20that%20naturally.%20Select%20a%20sunny%20to%20partially%20shaded%20area%2C%20it%20can%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noope